cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with dense tracking using convolutional feature maps from a pre-trained CNN. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of dense SLAM systems for camera rotation tracking experiments. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses a pre-trained CNN for feature extraction. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with scene representation for real-time visual SLAM. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with tracking in time-lapse sequences captured over many hours.
